Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像自己正在飛然後保持平衡！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 妮帕前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平衡！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 妮帕前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛 為什麼在這裡會有油罐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎 莎夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我罰跪！
